        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> 2. Add multiple sinks to a logger.\n\nI have not considered this for now, but it should be very easy to implement.\n\n> (Also important we can append sinks to the list without nuking the plugin authors sink since the plugin author may not export the sink)\n\nI do not think this is something we need to worry about, because plugin authors may also fail to add logs in the places users need. After all, We cannot force them how to use this module. But in both cases, what is missing is just a simple PR for the plugin. And it is still possible to implement it on top of this PR.\n\nI think what we need to focus on now is keeping the module’s interface stable while making it flexible enough to leave room for future improvements, rather than trying to complete every possible feature we can think of in a single PR.",
